videos.description: Cam Thomas fakes the handoff and bursts for a 23-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Illinois' Thomas gets into the end zone untouched

videos.description: Bennett Williams tips Clayton Thorson's pass to himself and returns it 15 yards.
videos.headline: Illinois snatches interception on 3rd-and-goal

videos.description: Clayton Thorson hits Garrett Dickerson for an 11-yard touchdown to tie the score at 7-7.
videos.headline: Northwestern's Dickerson grabs game-tying TD

videos.description: Dre Brown goes full speed for a 49-yard kickoff return to midfield.
videos.headline: Brown gets Illinois in good field position with 49-yard return

videos.description: Clayton Thorson completes a pass to Bennett Skowronek for 52 yards to set up a touchdown.
videos.headline: Northwestern's Skowronek outleaps defender for 52-yard completion

videos.description: Jelani Roberts goes around the edge for a 5-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Northwestern's Roberts scored TD on jet sweep

videos.description: Dre Brown shows his speed again and races to the end zone for a 50-yard kickoff return.
videos.headline: Illinois' Brown gets another big return

videos.description: Joe Gaziano strip sacks Cam Thomas and Sam Miller scoops up the loose ball for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Strip sack results in Northwestern TD

videos.description: Justin Jackson takes the handoff and streaks down the sideline for 79-yard run.
videos.headline: Northwestern's Jackson scampers for 79-yard run

videos.description: Justin Jackson barrels into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jackson finishes 2-play drive with TD

videos.description: Jeremy Larkin fights through two defenders for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Northwestern's Larkin powers into end zone

videos.description: Trae Williams picks off Cam Thomas' pass and returns it 65 yards to Illinois' 13-yard line.
videos.headline: Northwestern returns interception for 65 yards

videos.description: A flurry of flags fly on the field and Illinois DL Tito Odenigbo takes one of the flags and flings it back at the official earning himself an ejection.
